SELECT count(*) as aggregate FROM (SELECT `articles`.`id`, `articles`.`image`, `articles`.`title`, `articles`.`slug`, `articles`.`catalogue_id`, `articles`.`userid_created`, `articles`.`created_at`, `articles`.`publish`, `articles`.`order`, `articles`.`ishome`, `articles`.`highlight`, `articles`.`isaside`, `articles`.`isfooter` FROM `articles` inner join `catalogues_relationships` on `articles`.`id` = `catalogues_relationships`.`moduleid` WHERE (`alanguage` = 'vi' and `type` = 0) and `catalogues_relationships`.`module` = 'articles' GROUP BY `catalogues_relationships`.`moduleid`) as `aggregate_table`
